Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You all know that every app,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,even your app, needs an app
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,icon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the symbol that represents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your product on the Home screen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity has been using symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to communicate ideas since
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,antiquity; even Apple was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only joking, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope there are no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,egyptologists [phonetic] in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,room that were offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But in all seriousness, we have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a long rich history of using
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,symbols, literal, non-literal,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as a method of communication,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we extend this to the modern
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,world, but we apply the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,principles to the user interface
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,design.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, there was your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Macintosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a quick trip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,down memory lane and take a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,closer look at some classic Mac
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,OS icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Many metaphors have stuck around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for three decades of Mac OS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Investing in simple application
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,iconography was a way to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,emotionally relate to the user.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It made the system approachable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and easy to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It also made the platform unique
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand apart from the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Many are close approximations of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,real world objects, and some
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,concepts might be a little on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the abstract side, but they all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,live within a system that tells
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a user that they're
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,interconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, they're
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate; some are families,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,like families of maps or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,families of documents, and due
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to time, we've moved beyond some
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,metaphors, either because the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,technology was surpassed, like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the floppy disc; remember those,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or the metaphor we're seeing is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,too aggressive, like the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we had to learn a concept
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,like the hieroglyph .
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Over time the face was removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've come to notice there's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just the explanation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even smaller glyphs share the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,same principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a close look at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my personal favorites,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the paint bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The paint bucket fills your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,canvas with color, just like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,spilling a real can of paint on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, this was an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,abstract idea, but it was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,grounded here by a real world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,object.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And how about how this was drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even in those days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider the consistency of line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's implied movement in the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,angle, a subtle indication of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a good balance of black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple and high contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These examples represent some
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,fundamental principles that we
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,still use today when designing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,app icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The first, metaphor, finding an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,easily identifiable metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that will object or graphic logo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The second, simplicity; your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,design should be simple and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,clear, no clutter or over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,complicate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If your icon is designed well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it should be quick and easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,read.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiming to create an emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,connection with the user, the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,icon is the face of your app as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,much as the UI.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it fun, keep it engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And lineage, make changes to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,your icon meaningful and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't change your app icon every
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,single time that you update your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Refine your identity over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's think about some of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,these principles as they related
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to an Apple app.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keynote. Since version 1, all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the way back in 2003, the app's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,identity has been the podium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And why the podium, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the symbology is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,important, especially today of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a real old metaphor that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,many can relate to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Presenters have used podiums for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,generations, and to add an
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,emotional connection, the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,presenter notes rest on a warm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,wooden surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The microphone adds a familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It immediately sets the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for what keynote does, and we
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't want to lose that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As keynote has moved from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,version to version, we updated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the materials, and we've
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,transitioned from a classic to a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,modern style, but the notion of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the podium has remained
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The lineage provides users with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a sense of familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The podium was such a strong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,mark that when we designed our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,apps for iOS, we simplified the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,podium to more of a glyph and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,brought it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The visual connection here is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,really important because it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,tells users that they can expect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at consistent experience across
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,platforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you have a family of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,apps, take a look at the iLook
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Keynote uses the podium on both
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mac and iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pages uses the pen, a metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for writing and the written
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The paper is denoted by a line
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on iOS but helps to ground the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,pen to a surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers uses a flat and more 2D
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,representation of the chart and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the table on iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We extend the same principles to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,GarageBand with, and iMovie with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the guitar and the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The metaphor in color palettes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of these actually share
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the cross platform to reinforce
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea of family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's focus in on a few details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things are super important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, the colors harmonize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with the rest of iOSs vibrant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,color palette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The glyphs are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They all share the same mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're white and high contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,details, and they all share the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,same ground plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This might just look like the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keynote podium, but there are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,some subtle optimizations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,within.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, the corners are all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,custom curves, so they appear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,really smooth, a large and small
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, again, the same principles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,metaphor, simplicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,connection, lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at these as they
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,relate to another app, music
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,memo, shown here on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a clear connection to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the history of GarageBand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,through color and metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The circle is reminiscent of a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sound hole in an acoustic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The strings vibrate in a playful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,graphic way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a sense of movement and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,creativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The icon makes use of the iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,icon grid so that when music
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,memos appears next to other
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,icons in the system, the common
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,elements like the circle are the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,same size as say Safari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we're going to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a little fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a look at
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the News app icon to look at
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the more practical
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,considerations to think of when
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you design your app icon and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,some tests that you can do at
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,home to make sure that your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,design is holding up at a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller size.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's ask ourselves a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,question, in a hypothetical
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,world, what if News were the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,only app on the home screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What would the icon have to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,communicate for it to be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately clear that News does
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what News actually does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to be understood without a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,name underneath the icon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How would a good use of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,simplicity, form, color,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,contrast, composition help it to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,be understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think an icon would have to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,work twice as hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here's a few other props
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that we tried along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The first icon here has a peak
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of paper is a little abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the end rest on a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper, or a white box?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A little hard to tell, and much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of the red background is hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The second introduces another
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,sheet behind the first, which
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,helps to reinforce the metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,a little, but when the other
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,edges are missing, you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,tell that the N is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,resting on a newspaper, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,color is still fairly hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the third design.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can clearly see all the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,edges on the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The white is high contrast; the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,red background pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The rendering of the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and logo text is simple, bold,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and graphic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you look at your icon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Home screen, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,really see what holds up at a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,small size and is the right mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for contrast form and color.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the three designs at a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,small size.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And try testing your icon in a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,folder next to other icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Squint your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the news article?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there on the top left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's easy to see because of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the simple design.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The composition is distinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's high contrast, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,color is clearly visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing an app icon is an
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,iterative process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's some other things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could think about as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you start to design yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start with the first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to be unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that might sound like a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,tall order, but it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to be really aware of other apps
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in your category.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the three apps in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,video space, Quick, Instagram,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Periscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at how different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,these icons are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Colors and shapes are bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Each is distinct; it stands out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Home screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Instagram is also a great
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,example of how an icon can
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,become synonymous with a company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment you see the white
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,camera glyph, the purple sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you immediately think Instagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, despite how beautiful a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,blank canvas is, starting here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,might be a little daunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why not try a little bit of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,sketching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't think you can
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,raw, sometimes a pen and paper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,goes way further than a mouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and sketching is a great way to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,get your ideas out without
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying about finessing your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,icon early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do some doodles; show your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,friends; get their ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your app icon, so your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,design has to pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some fun with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Further, and perhaps most
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,important, test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we mean by test?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you develop your app
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,icon, examine on the Home
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,screen, in a folder, and if your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,app has settings, the settings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And be careful if you decide to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,represent your user interface in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,your icon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear is a great example of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,doing this really, really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got a strong visual
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,style with recognizable colors
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and a simple brand of pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that really helps to stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at a small size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, it's simple, colorful,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,high contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And last but not least, have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,some patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer might not come to you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time, examine your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,options, and save your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oftentimes, it's the simplest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,design or an early direction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that you abandoned that you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,actually ultimately find is the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to summarize, when designing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,your app icon, think about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,metaphor, a clearly identifiable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,object or symbol that is simple
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To create an emotional
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,connection with the user, be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,fun, be playful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And lineage, your icon is the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,face of your app.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of your icon as an
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the process, try to make
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,your icon unique so it stands
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,out on the Home screen and the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,App Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiment with different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,designs and test them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the icon grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at icons that Apple has
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,designed as reference for form
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See what looks good, big and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your icon in a folder to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how it looks at a really small
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,size.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to optimize
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your assets for different device
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing an app icon can seem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,like a lot of work, but if you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,invest the time to do it, it can
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,really, really pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your time.
